page.title: 22Wyvern Tech collage
page.content:
Wyvern is in the fair oak schools campus the timetable are arranged through your band the head teacher is called Mr A. Newton and each year is divided into 21 tutors which you see 4 days a week at the start of the school day at 8:30 and on the other day the whole year goes into the hall for a assembly
Nick Eddy
